  LIST OF GAMES
ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄ

      SRE - Solar Realms Elite
            0.990   latest release version

            SRE is this game!

      AC6 - Alpha Colony 6
            0.950 - latest release

            AC6 is similar to SRE in style & play.  It's written by a
            different programmer in a different language; it's not exactly
            the same; it takes many of the same types of actions and extends
            them (12 types of attack instead of 5, using multiple covert
            agents in a covert op, and stocks are just some examples).
            It is not well-supported, and it still has many bugs.

      PC  - Planetary Conquest
            1.2 - latest release, but the executable says "1.1"
            PC is no longer supported.  Registrations are not accepted.

            Planetary Conquest is a strategy game placed on a 20x20 on-screen
            board.  There are several playing pieces, each with a different
            purpose, strength, move, and weapon.  There are Soldiers, Tanks,
            Bases, Artillery, Walls, Obstacles/Symbols, and Water.  There are
            20 scenarios that can be played by 4 players, and additional
            scenarios are available on our board.

      SCE - Solar Conquests Elite
            1.1 - latest release
            SCE is no longer supported.  Registrations are not accepted.

            Solar Conquests Elite is similar to PC, but is based in space.
            There are 5 types of ships and several weapon/engine types.
            The game allows from 2 to 5 players to play.

      LEA - Lost Empires of Arcadia
            0.990 - latest release
            LEA is not currently supported.  Registrations are not accepted.

            Lost Empires of Arcadia is a huge game with lots of races of
            beings, castles, thieves, wizards, assassins, many types of
            warfare, etc.  There are of course, many bugs!  :(

      SRH - Solar Realms Hangman
            0.990 - latest release

            This is a computer version of the popular 'Hangman' game.  You
            can enter words and other players have to guess them.  The winner
            gets to enter another word or phrase, and the process continues.

      BRE - Barren Realms Elite
            0.900 - latest releases change every day, so I don't have the
            right version number.

            This is a brand-new game that is better than SRE, not only in
            play, but in allowing you to play against other BBSes through
            Fidonet.  There are more covert ops, more trading options, a
            trading market, better warfare, nicer news files, and best of
            all - Inter-BBS operations!

